                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-391a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T01:50:32.938+09:00">If he conforms to the point of complete agreement,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-391a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T01:50:54.593+09:00">he will be ruined and no longer be in a position to provide reform,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-391a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T01:51:46.694+09:00">and thus will be destroyed together with him [the hir to the throne, Kuaikui].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-391a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T03:22:50.138+09:00">Therefore, he should emulate Heaven and Earth,</seg>
